    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware the Obstacles as you Fling D’Block!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fling D'Block</strong> is a physics-based precision time trial and speedrunning game that puts your skills to the ultimate test. Propel and bounce your block through a series of treacherous levels, striving to achieve the fastest time possible. Along the way, collect valuable crystals, navigate perilous obstacles, and avoid fatal mistakes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This fast-paced game challenges your speed, dexterity, and strategy as you master each level. Sharpen your reflexes, optimize your routes, and race to the exit with flawless precision. Can you conquer the clock and claim your spot as the ultimate speedrunner? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And whatever you do… Go as Fast as You Can!</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Traverse</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fling and bounce across perilous levels as you learn to master movement over time and dedication. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/1f424cad45f33907929511f5f49410fd.poster.avif?t=1732179625\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/1f424cad45f33907929511f5f49410fd.webm?t=1732179625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/1f424cad45f33907929511f5f49410fd.mp4?t=1732179625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Avoid</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spikes, Death Wheels, Spiked Pendulums, Auto-Tracking Turrets, and Spinning Lasers. There are dangers all around you so be careful where you fling. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/657a13456dd819aa6a115eb23cc40ffa.poster.avif?t=1732179625\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/657a13456dd819aa6a115eb23cc40ffa.webm?t=1732179625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/657a13456dd819aa6a115eb23cc40ffa.mp4?t=1732179625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fling D’Block comes with a built-in level editor for those of you that wish to create fun, exciting and challenging custom levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/d15da48a78a7b28dcc983c12ff119329.poster.avif?t=1732179625\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/d15da48a78a7b28dcc983c12ff119329.webm?t=1732179625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303770/extras/d15da48a78a7b28dcc983c12ff119329.mp4?t=1732179625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
